title: 40 for 40: The 2018 Birmingham through Hawaii Bowls
description:
Yup, still doing these. Nope, not particularly close to done yet. Eh, not really sure what we feel like having for dinner tonight. Maybe soup, but like a hearty soup? But not a creamy soup. Makes us all congested. Topics on this episode:
3:35 - THE BIRMINGHAM BOWL
19:45 - THE ARMED FORCES BOWL
29:27 - THE DOLLAR GENERAL BOWL
35:02 - THE HAWAII BOWL
